//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Soccer-Mommy-Anna-Pollack-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Soccer-Mommy-Anna-Pollack-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soccer-mommy">足球妈妈</a>分享了新单曲“Driver”以及 2025 年英国头条巡演的详细信息。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="367" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/soccer-mommy-new-album-sometimes-forever-oneohtrix-point-never-3252194"><b>足球妈妈抵制音乐行业的废话：“当你讨厌它时，这很容易”</b></a></li></ul><p>八月，纳什维尔歌手兼词曲作者——真名索菲亚·艾利森——宣布推出她即将发行的专辑《Evergreen》，标志着她阔别两年后的回归。期待已久的 2022 年《Sometimes, Forever》的后续作品将于 10 月 25 日通过 Loma Vista Recordings 发布<a href="https://lnk.soccermommyband.com/EG" target="_blank" rel="noopener">。您可以在此处预订</a>。</p><p>最新单曲是一首对优柔寡断和妥协的大气颂歌，延续了之前版本的“M”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soccer-mommy-returns-with-new-single-lost-3763301">“Lost”。</a>在最近的美国巡演中展示了后者后，她上个月分享了这首歌曲将作为新专辑的开场曲目。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="足球妈妈 - Driver（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/y9t0YjNb0dI?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>根据一份新闻稿，这张专辑是由“深刻且非常个人的损失”塑造的。与制作人 Ben H. Allen III（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/deerhunter">《Deerhunter》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/belle-and-sebastian">《Belle &amp; Sebastian</a> 》）一起在亚特兰大的 Maze Studios 录制，高亢的情感导致了声音的目标是尽可能忠实于“原始且相关”的演示，歌曲创作控制着“生产将随之而来”。</p><h3><strong>足球妈妈的“长青”曲目列表是：</strong></h3><ol><li> <strong>&#39;丢失的&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="368" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;M&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="368" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>&#39;司机&#39;</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="368" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>《某个阳光明媚的日子》</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="368" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="2" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“改变”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="368" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quo