.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Refused.-Credit-Tim-Tronckoe-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Refused.-Credit-Tim-Tronckoe-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Refused.-Credit-Tim-Tronckoe-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Refused">Refused</a>确认分手，并宣布推出第三张专辑《The Shape Of Punk To Come》25 周年纪念版。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/refused-war-music-review-2558630">拒绝——“战争音乐”评论：朋克一切辉煌的缩影</a></strong></li></ul><p>1998 年，在支持《The Shape Of Punk To Come》的北美巡演期间，这支瑞典朋克乐队解散了，但在 2012 年重新组合，并发行了 2015 年的《Freedom》和 2019 年的《War Music》。今天（9月10日），乐队宣布正式解散，Refused乐队正式结束。</p><p>乐队的鼓手 David Sandström 在一份新闻稿中证实了乐队的分手，他表示乐队最初打算在今年早些时候宣布解散，从他们在斯德哥尔摩的罗森达尔花园派对上的头条新闻开始，这场派对被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/refused-announce-last-festival-performance-in-sweden-as-band-look-to-wind-down-3598119">宣传为“他们在瑞典的最后一场音乐节演出”。曾经。”</a> </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CJG2S8bjy8O/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12p